        <section id="about" class="about">
        <h1>About</h1>
        <p>Hollow Knight is a 2D, action-adventure Metroidvania game developed by Team Cherry.
            In this game, you explore the dark, vast land of Hallownest, facing difficult and memorable enemies
            as you try to put together the reason for why you are there.</p>
    </section>
