    <section id="review" class="review">
        <h1>Review</h1>
        <p>Hollow Knight is easily one of my favorite games. Besides being an fair yet challenging adventure, the world is incredibly well made.
            It is fun exploring the nooks and crannies of the world trying to figure out the story of the game while happening upon sudden, exhilarating battles.
            Besides the gameplay and story, the completely hand-drawn art and beautifully made music is inspiring and sets the atmosphere perfectly.</p>
    </section>
